name: Trade Federation Landing Craft
Lore: 'C-9979 landing craft designed to transport and unload Multi Troop Transports and its battle droid cargo as rapidly as possible.',
Text: 'May add 2 pilots and 6 vehicles. Deploys and moves like a starfighter. While at a site, once during your deploy phase may take an MTT into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
